<task id="task_742EE5B342B44C749B02A945FEB81D83">
  <title>Revenue Per Click</title>
  <shortdesc>Use a redirector to pass the revenue per click. 
  </shortdesc>
  <prolog>
    <metadata>
      <othermeta name="solution" content="Target" />
      <othermeta name="topic" content="Advanced" />
    </metadata>
  </prolog>
  <taskbody>
    <context id="context_D759251F4C714EAEAED699358C91FC95">
      <p>
        <note>Best practice is to determine the revenue value using the 
			 <b>Score per visit</b> engagement metric, as described in 
			 <xref href="c_Capturing_Engagement.xml#concept_DB31E18F26EA426EB7A87EAE16A477A5" type="concept" format="dita" scope="local"><?xm-replace_text Capturing Engagement?></xref>.
			 
		  </note>
      </p>
      <p>Add 
		  <codeph>&amp;mboxPageValue=value</codeph> to the URL. 
		</p>
      <p>Example: For a .10 cents revenue per click. 
		</p>
      <p>
        <codeblock outputclass="syntax html">http://&lt;​your_clientcode&gt;​​​​.tt​​.omtrdc​.net/​​m2/​yourclientcode/​ubox/​​​page?mbox=redirectorlink_456
&amp;mboxPageValue=0.1​&amp;mbox​Default=​​http%3A%2F%2Fwww%2E​yourcompany%2Ecom​%2Fusualdestination%2Ehtm</codeblock>
      </p>
      <p>See 
		  <xref href="c_Cost_and_Revenue_Reporting.xml#concept_A07BEDC4725F4887B6301C1B9FC3D1C8" type="concept" format="dita" scope="local"><?xm-replace_text Cost and Revenue Reporting?></xref>
		  for more information. 
		</p>
    </context>
  </taskbody>
